  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a wok or large frying pan over high heat.",
    "Add beef and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Remove beef from the pan and set aside.",
    "In the same pan, add minced garlic, onion, red bell pepper, celery sticks, and shallots.",
